data.description: BACK ON MARKET!! Hidden gem in the quiet gated community of Village at James Street! This 1-story condo features a light & bright open design w/vaulted ceilings, oversized windows & fresh interior paint throughout. Spacious kitchen w/light cabinets, ample storage, ample counter space, breakfast nook & all appliances stay! Primary suite w/dual closets & an en-suite boasting a walk-in shower. Additional features include a sizable guest bedroom, full bath off main living space & fireplace. Individual 1-car garage, private landscaped yard & just steps to Green River Trail. Community amenities include a large clubhouse, hot tub, pool, exercise room & sports court. Mins from Hwy 167/I5, light rail/Kent Station, parks, golf course & amenities.
